<!-- ===== FEATURED COURSES (LIVE FROM DB) ===== -->
<section class="section section-alt" id="courses">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header-row" data-animate="fade-up">
      <div>
        <p class="section-label">Course Catalog</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Featured programmes</h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/courses" class="btn btn-ghost">View all courses &#8594;</a>
    </div>
    <% if (featuredCourses.length) { %>
    <div class="catalog-carousel" data-catalog-carousel>
      <button type="button" class="catalog-nav catalog-nav-prev" data-carousel-prev aria-label="Previous">&#8249;</button>
      <div class="catalog-viewport">
        <div class="catalog-track" data-carousel-track>
          <% featuredCourses.forEach(function(course) { %>
          <div class="catalog-slide">
            <a href="/courses/<%= course.id %>" class="course-card-link" data-animate="fade-up">
              <article class="course-card">
                <div class="course-img course-img-<%= (course.id % 9) + 1 %> <%= course.image ? 'has-course-image' : '' %>"<% if (course.image) { %> style="--course-image: url('<%= course.image %>');"<% } %>>
                  <div class="course-category-tag"><%= course.category || 'General' %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="course-body">
                  <h3 class="course-title"><%= course.title %></h3>
                  <p class="course-description"><%= course.description %></p>
                  <div class="course-footer">
                    <span class="course-meta-pill">Professional Programme</span>
                    <span class="course-arrow">&#8594;</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </article>
            </a>
          </div>
          <% }); %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button type="button" class="catalog-nav catalog-nav-next" data-carousel-next aria-label="Next">&#8250;</button>
    </div>
    <% } else { %>
    <div class="course-empty" data-animate="fade-up">
      <h3>No courses available yet</h3>
      <p>The course catalog is currently being prepared.</p>
      <a href="/courses" class="btn btn-primary">Open Courses Page</a>
    </div>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== WHY OSIAN / FAQ ===== -->
<section class="section faq-section" id="why">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="faq-layout">
      <div class="faq-left" data-animate="fade-up">
        <p class="section-label">Why Choose Osian</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">What Makes Us Different</h2>
        <p class="faq-sub">Osian Academy is built on a simple belief: every learner deserves personal attention. Here's how we deliver on that promise.</p>
        <div class="faq-highlight">
          <div class="faq-hl-item">
            <span class="faq-hl-num">500+</span>
            <span class="faq-hl-text">Satisfied Students</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-hl-item">
            <span class="faq-hl-num">100%</span>
            <span class="faq-hl-text">Live Sessions</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-hl-item">
            <span class="faq-hl-num">5+</span>
            <span class="faq-hl-text">Years Experience</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-hl-item">
            <span class="faq-hl-num">95%</span>
            <span class="faq-hl-text">Satisfaction Rate</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-right" data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay:.1s">
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item open" data-faq-item>
            <button class="faq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="true">
              <span>What makes Osian Academy different from other platforms?</span>
              <span class="faq-arrow">&#8964;</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a">
              <p>Unlike platforms that offer pre-recorded lectures to thousands simultaneously, Osian delivers every session live and 1-on-1. Your dedicated instructor knows your progress, adapts to your pace, and answers questions in real time. No batch-based classes, no generic content.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item" data-faq-item>
            <button class="faq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Who are the instructors at Osian Academy?</span>
              <span class="faq-arrow">&#8964;</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a">
              <p>All Osian instructors are working professionals with a minimum of 5 years of industry experience. They go through a rigorous selection process — only the top applicants are accepted. You learn from people who actively do the work, not just teach it.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item" data-faq-item>
            <button class="faq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
              <span>How do 1-on-1 sessions work exactly?</span>
              <span class="faq-arrow">&#8964;</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a">
              <p>After enrolment, you're matched with an instructor based on your goals and schedule. Sessions are conducted on our online platform — you collaborate in real time, share screens, and can pause or revisit any topic. Sessions are typically 60–90 minutes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item" data-faq-item>
            <button class="faq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
              <span>What certifications will I receive upon completion?</span>
              <span class="faq-arrow">&#8964;</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a">
              <p>You receive an Osian Academy certification that is verifiable online. For select courses, we also prepare you for globally recognised third-party certifications — AWS, Google, Microsoft, and CompTIA. All credentials are added to your Osian profile and shareable on LinkedIn.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item" data-faq-item>
            <button class="faq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Is there career support after I complete a programme?</span>
              <span class="faq-arrow">&#8964;</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a">
              <p>Yes — career support is included in all programmes. This covers resume review, LinkedIn profile optimisation, mock interviews with industry professionals, and access to our hiring partner network. Your instructor also provides mentorship as you begin your job search.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item" data-faq-item>
            <button class="faq-q" data-faq-question aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Can I learn at my own pace and on my own schedule?</span>
              <span class="faq-arrow">&#8964;</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a">
              <p>Absolutely. Because sessions are 1-on-1, the curriculum is fully flexible. Need more time on a topic? Your instructor adapts. Moving quickly? They'll push further. There is no fixed cohort schedule — just you and your instructor, moving at the right pace for you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

